                    <span>I read this book about ten years ago, when I was searching for truth.  This book did little to help that - I can remember nothing of value from this book.
<br />
<br />If you are searching for truth, read the Bible.  It is truth, and nothing will come close to it.
<br />
<br />Also, for an easier read than other translations, check out the NIV version.
<br />
<br />Thanks,
<br />Calvin</span>
                  
